Name: Speedrun
About the game: About speedrun Speedrun is a 2D platform game that you can jump, dash and move to dodge a dangerous spike that can kill you. You have to survive a dangerous underground city with your special movement! About the game play You will use a dash movement to go places that you will not able to go with the normal movement skills. and Also you can use a jump and move to have additional support in your movement.
